1. Information We Collect
As of now, we do not collect or store any personal information from users within the app.

The app allows users to:

Track their mood

View statistics and graphs

Use a cognitive restructuring tool (CBT form)

All of this data is stored locally on your device and is not sent to any server or shared with any third party.

2. Account Creation
If you choose to sign up or log in, we use AWS Cognito for authentication. This may involve basic information such as your email or username for login purposes only. We do not access or use this data for any other purpose.

3. Data Sharing
We do not share any user data with third parties.

4. Data Deletion
If you choose to delete your account, all associated data will be permanently deleted and cannot be recovered.

